-- ED&F Man Said to Hire FCStone’s Fincham as Asia Commodities Head
-- B y   A g n i e s z k a   T r o s z k i e w i c z
-- 2012-06-11T13:58:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-11/ed-f-man-said-to-hire-fcstone-s-fincham-as-asia-commodities-head.html
ED&F Man  Capital Markets  Ltd., a
unit of ED&F Man Holdings Ltd., hired Jane Ding Fincham as
managing director for the Asian region for metals, commodity and
futures markets, according to two people with direct knowledge.  Fincham will be based in London, said the people, who
declined to be named because the information hasn’t been made
public. She was previously head of INTL FCStone Inc.’s
commodities and London Metal Exchange business for Asia Pacific.  ED&F Man Capital Markets is one of 12 companies that
trade on the floor of the LME. Daniel Friend, ED&F Man’s
communications manager, wasn’t immediately available for
comment. Kent Coughlin, a spokesman for INTL FCStone, wasn’t
immediately able to comment.  To contact the reporter on this story:
